name: Beauty & Brillo 004
description: Meet Calypso, he comes from a futuristic tropics. She is very close friends with Coral. The two met on a trip to Los Cayos, Venezuela and created good memories that connect them today and make them think of those happy times while diving and meeting starfish. Calypso loves technology and believes in a world where it helps us connect new ways with nature. Collect this piece to be part of its tropikal universe.
